column3: Even though this is already merged, post merge ACKs are very welcome for this pull.

Reviewers may wish to git-show all of the commits listed, ensure they
are on the history of current trusted master, and make sure they are,
indeed, signed by one of Pieter's now-revoked subkeys.

Matt
